Overview

This dashboard shows Indicator overview related to the ThreatConnect Integration.

This dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the detection of ingested indicators.

It provides details on overall indicators and their respective groups. Additionally, it showcases the categorization of indicators based on type and owner. The dashboard includes a breakdown of associated groups by type and status, indicator attributes categorized by type, indicators rated by rating and confidence levels. The report encompasses information on the count of indicators over time. Furthermore, it features the top 10 IP addresses, accessed URLs, and host details, along with associated groups and owners linked to each indicator.
